          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This method finds nodes that are part of the grid created by the graph. You can attach other nodes to the graph (for example, to represent the positions of game entities in the grid) with the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gameplaykit/documentation/GameplayKit/GKGridGraph/connectToAdjacentNodes(node:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method, but such nodes are not part of the grid itself.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
